
An attempt to convert a "corporate" document into a LeTeX document. 



Features
========
   - custom cover page
   - customized text on cover page
   - personalized header and footer
   - personalize title presentation
   - vertical filigrane on every page
   - tweak document font
To do
=====

   - add custom commands to improve reusability of the template


